  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a developper, I want to be able to leverage all web technologies in my DApp.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nSome web API usages require user permission (usually some popup a user has to confirm).\r\nThose API should be available to DApps authors.\r\n\r\nAs we already asks specific user permission (e.g. camera) it would be great to reuse those and not asks for already granted permission.\r\n\r\nAt least media permissions should be working and the following site should be usable: https://davidwalsh.name/demo/camera.php\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n",
